name: Material Transfer Unit-1
query:
select
    se.stock_entry_type as 'Stock Entry Type',
    
    
	se.posting_date as "Posting Date",
	se_item.s_warehouse as "From Warehouse",
	se_item.t_warehouse as "To Warehouse",
    se_item.item_code as "Item Name:Link/Item:120",
    se_item.qty as "Qty:Float:100"
from
	`tabStock Entry` se, `tabStock Entry Detail` se_item

where
	se.name = se_item.parent 
	and
    se.stock_entry_type = "Material Transfer"
    and
    se.company = "Khetan Udyog"
AND
 (
       DATE(se.posting_date) between %(from_date) s
       and %(to_date) s
   )

name: Daily Production Report Unit-2
query:
with finish as( Select fq.qty, 
fq.item_name, fq.parent from 
`tabStock Entry` fp  left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` fq on fq.parent = fp.name
where fq.is_finished__item = 1 AND fp.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2"), 
scrap as(Select sq.qty,sq.parent from `tabStock Entry` sp 
left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` sq on sq.parent = sp.name 
where sq.is_scrap_item= 1 AND sp.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2"),
reject as(Select rq.qty,rq.parent from `tabStock Entry` rp
 left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` rq on rq.parent = rp.name 
where rq.rejected_item = 1 AND rp.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2")

Select DISTINCT
p.posting_date as "Posting Date",
p.shift_type as "Shift",
p.manufacturing_type as "Manufacturing Type",
p.machine as "Machine",
p.operation as "Operation",
p.supervisor_name as "Supervisor Name",
p.senior_operator_name as "Senior Operator Name",
p.operator_name as "Operator Name",
finish.item_name as "Finished Item",
IFNULL(finish.qty, 0) as "Finished Qty", 
IFNULL(scrap.qty,0) as "Scrap Qty",
IFNULL(reject.qty, 0) as "Reject Qty"

 

from `tabStock Entry` p left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` q on q.parent = p.name 
left outer join finish on finish.parent=p.name 
left outer join scrap on scrap.parent=p.name 
left outer join reject on reject.parent=p.name
where  q.s_warehouse IS NOT NULL AND p.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2"
and p.docstatus = 1 
AND ( DATE(p.posting_date) between %(from_date) s and %(to_date) s ) 


 ORDER BY p.`posting_date` DESC

name: Operator Wise Material Tracking Unit-2
query:
with finish as( Select fq.qty, 
fq.item_name, fq.basic_rate, fq.parent from 
`tabStock Entry` fp  left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` fq on fq.parent = fp.name
where fq.is_finished__item = 1 AND fp.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2 "), 
scrap as(Select sq.qty,sq.parent from `tabStock Entry` sp 
left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` sq on sq.parent = sp.name 
where sq.is_scrap_item= 1 AND sp.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2"),
reject as(Select rq.qty,rq.parent from `tabStock Entry` rp
 left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` rq on rq.parent = rp.name 
where rq.rejected_item = 1 AND rp.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2"),
operator as(select op.operator_name, op.item_name, op.qty, op.machine, op.basic_rate from
`tabStock Entry` left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` as op on  `tabStock Entry`.name = op.parent
where `tabStock Entry`.stock_entry_type ='Material Issue'),
straightner as(Select sq.qty,sq.parent from `tabStock Entry` sp 
left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` sq on sq.parent = sp.name 
where sq.straightner= 1 AND sp.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2"),
short_length as(Select sq.qty,sq.parent from `tabStock Entry` sp 
left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` sq on sq.parent = sp.name 
where sq.short_length= 1 AND sp.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2")


Select DISTINCT
p.posting_date as " Date",
operator.machine as "Issue Machine Name",
p.operator_name as "Operator Name",
operator.item_name as "Material Issue Item Name",
operator.qty as "Material Issue Qty",
operator.basic_rate as "Issue Rate",
p.machine as "Machine Name",
 finish.item_name as "Finished Item",
IFNULL(finish.qty, 0) as "Finished Qty",
IFNULL(finish.basic_rate, 0) as "Finished Rate",
IFNULL(scrap.qty,0) as "Scrap Qty",
IFNULL(reject.qty, 0) as "Reject Qty",
IFNULL(straightner.qty,0) as "Straightner Qty",
IFNULL(short_length.qty, 0) as "Short Length Qty"
 

from 
operator,
`tabStock Entry` p left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` q on q.parent = p.name 
left outer join finish on finish.parent=p.name 
left outer join scrap on scrap.parent=p.name 
left outer join reject on reject.parent=p.name
left outer join straightner on straightner.parent = p.name
left outer join short_length on short_length.parent = p.name
where  q.s_warehouse IS NOT NULL AND p.stock_entry_type = "Manufacturing Unit-2"
and p.docstatus = 1 

and
p.operator = operator.operator_name

AND
(
       DATE(p.posting_date) between %(from_date) s
       and %(to_date) s
   )
and p.`operator` = %(p.operator)s


 ORDER BY p.`posting_date` DESC

name: Attendance Comparision Report
query: SELECT DISTINCT    at.attendance_date AS "Attendance Date",    at.employee AS "Employee Id",    at.employee_name AS "Employee Name",    at.status AS "Status",    at.new_hours AS "Working Hours",    NULL AS "Card Status",    card.card_working_hours AS "Card Working Hours",    NULL AS "Hour Difference"    FROM    `tabAttendance` AS atLEFT JOIN    `tabCard Attendance` AS cardON    at.employee_name = card.employee_name    AND at.attendance_date = card.attendance_date    AND at.company = card.companyWHERE    at.company = "SANTOSH UNIT 2"    AND card.name IS NULL    AND DATE(at.attendance_date) BETWEEN %(from_date)s AND %(to_date)sUNIONSELECT DISTINCT    card.attendance_date AS "Attendance Date",    card.employee AS "Employee Id",    card.employee_name AS "Employee Name",    NULL AS "Status",    NULL AS "Working Hours",    card.card_status AS "Card Status",    card.card_working_hours AS "Card Working Hours",    NULL AS "Hour Difference"    FROM    `tabAttendance` AS atRIGHT JOIN    `tabCard Attendance` AS cardON    at.employee_name = card.employee_name    AND at.attendance_date = card.attendance_date    AND at.company = card.companyWHERE    at.company IS NULL    AND DATE(card.attendance_date) BETWEEN %(from_date)s AND %(to_date)sUNIONSELECT DISTINCT    at.attendance_date AS "Attendance Date",    at.employee AS "Employee Id",    at.employee_name AS "Employee Name",    at.status AS "Status",    at.new_hours AS "Working Hours",    card.card_status AS "Card Status",    card.card_working_hours AS "Card Working Hours",    ROUND((card.card_working_hours - at.new_hours),2) AS "Hour Difference"    FROM    `tabAttendance` AS atINNER JOIN    `tabCard Attendance` AS cardON    at.employee_name = card.employee_name    AND at.attendance_date = card.attendance_date    AND at.company = card.companyWHERE    at.company = "SANTOSH UNIT 2"    AND DATE(at.attendance_date) BETWEEN %(from_date)s AND %(to_date)sORDER BY    "Attendance Date" DESC;

name: Material Transfer For Supplier
query: WITH voucher AS(    SELECT       `tabStock Entry`.name,        `tabStock Entry`.voucher_no,        `tabStock Entry`.returnable_or_non_returnable,        `tabStock Entry`.received_qty,         vd.qty,         vd.pending_qty_material_received,         `tabStock Entry`.posting_date            from        `tabStock Entry`        inner join `tabStock Entry Detail` as vd on  `tabStock Entry`.name = vd.parent    where        stock_entry_type ='Material Received for Supplier'        )select    se.stock_entry_type as 'Stock Entry Type',    se.party_name_ as 'Party Name',    se.name as 'Voucher No:Link/Stock Entry',    se.posting_date as 'Material Transfer Date',    se.returnable_or_non_returnable as 'Returnable Or Non Returnable',    sed.item_code as 'Item Name',    voucher.received_qty as 'In Qty',    voucher.qty as 'Out Qty',    voucher.pending_qty_material_received as 'Balance Qty',    voucher.name as 'Material Received For Supplier:Link/Stock Entry',    voucher.posting_date as 'Material Received Date'      from    voucher,    `tabStock Entry` se    join `tabStock Entry Detail` sedon sed.parent=se.namewhere    se.stock_entry_type = 'Material Transfer for Supplier'    and voucher.voucher_no = se.name          and (       DATE(se.posting_date) between %(from_date) s       and %(to_date) s   )unionselect    se.stock_entry_type,    se.party_name_,    se.name as 'Voucher No:Link/Stock Entry',    se.posting_date as 'Material Transfer Date',    se.returnable_or_non_returnable,    sed.item_code as 'Item Name',    null,    null,    null,    null,    null       from    voucher,    `tabStock Entry` se    join `tabStock Entry Detail` sedon sed.parent=se.namewhere    se.stock_entry_type =  'Material Transfer for Supplier'    and se.returnable_or_non_returnable = 'Returnable'    and se.docstatus = 1    and voucher.voucher_no != se.name         and (       DATE(se.posting_date) between %(from_date) s       and %(to_date) s   )unionselect    se.stock_entry_type,    se.party_name_,    se.name,    se.posting_date as 'Material Transfer Date',    se.returnable_or_non_returnable,    sed.item_code as 'Item Code',    null,    null,    null,    null,    null   from    voucher,    `tabStock Entry` se    join `tabStock Entry Detail` sedon sed.parent=se.namewhere    se.name in(        select            name        from            `tabStock Entry`        where            returnable_or_non_returnable = 'Non Returnable'                        and (       DATE(se.posting_date) between %(from_date) s       and %(to_date) s   )    )    and se.docstatus = 1

name: Subcontracting Received Material
query: WITH delivery AS(    SELECT     `tabDelivery Note`.name,     `tabDelivery Note`.posting_date,     `tabDelivery Note`.customer,      `tabDelivery Note`.total_qty,       vd.item_name   from        `tabDelivery Note`        left outer  join `tabDelivery Note Item` as vd on `tabDelivery Note`.name = vd.parent    )select     se.stock_entry_type as 'Stock Entry Type',    se.party,    delivery.name as 'Delivery Note:Link/Delivery Note',    delivery.item_name as 'Transfer Material',    delivery.total_qty as'Out Qty',    sed.item_name as 'Received Material',    sed.qty as 'In Qty',    sed.pending_qty as 'Balance Qty',    se.name as 'Stock Entry :Link/Stock Entry',    se.posting_date as 'Date'           from    delivery,    `tabStock Entry` se    left outer join `tabStock Entry Detail` sed    on sed.parent=se.namewherese.stock_entry_type="Subcontracting Received Material"and    se.docstatus =1              and (       DATE(se.posting_date) between %(from_date) s       and %(to_date) s   )    and delivery.name = se.delivery_note GROUP BY sed.item_name

name: Party Wise Sales Analytics
query:
select 
se.customer_name as "customer Name",
sed.item_code as "Item Code",
SUM(sed.qty) as "Total Qty",
COUNT(se.name) as "Total Transaction"
from `tabSales Order` se join `tabSales Order Item` sed on se.name = sed.parent
where
 (
       DATE(se.transaction_date) between %(from_date) s
       and %(to_date) s
   )

 and se.customer = %(se.customer)s
GROUP BY se.customer_name, sed.item_code

name: Quotation Order Report
query:
SELECT 
    qtc.item_code AS "Item Code",
    qtc.item_name AS "Item Name",
    sum(qtc.qty) AS "Quotation Qty",
    sum(slt.qty) AS "Sales Order Qty",
    (sum(sit.qty)) AS "Out Qty",
    (sum(slt.qty) - COALESCE(sum(sit.qty), 0)) AS "Invoice Pending Qty",
    COALESCE(bn_actual_qty_sum, 0) AS 'Actual Qty'
FROM `tabQuotation` qt
JOIN `tabQuotation Item` qtc ON qt.name = qtc.parent
LEFT OUTER JOIN `tabSales Order Item` slt ON qtc.item_code = slt.item_code AND qt.name = slt.prevdoc_docname
LEFT OUTER JOIN `tabSales Invoice Item` sit ON slt.item_code = sit.item_code 
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT item_code, SUM(CASE WHEN actual_qty > 0 THEN actual_qty ELSE 0 END) AS bn_actual_qty_sum
    FROM `tabBin`
    GROUP BY item_code
) bn ON qtc.item_code = bn.item_code 
WHERE
    DATE(qt.transaction_date) BETWEEN %(from_date)s AND %(to_date)s
    AND qt.company = "Khetan Udyog"
GROUP BY  qtc.item_code, qtc.item_name, bn_actual_qty_sum;

name: bin
query:
select
    item.item_code as "Item Code",
    sum((CASE WHEN  bn.actual_qty > 0 THEN bn.actual_qty ELSE 0 END)) AS 'Actual Qty'
from
 `tabItem` item 
join `tabBin` bn on bn.item_code = item.item_code
